WEBVTT

01:30.970 --> 01:35.020
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.860 --> 01:39.310
[2006]

01:39.680 --> 01:40.680
Auntie, I'm back.

01:40.680 --> 01:41.410
You're back.

01:41.870 --> 01:43.070
What are you holding?

01:44.310 --> 01:45.350
This is our group's entry

01:45.350 --> 01:47.350
for the architectural model competition.

01:47.350 --> 01:48.310
I didn't finish my part,

01:48.310 --> 01:49.970
so I brought it back to work on.

01:50.350 --> 01:51.920
You're a senior in high school now.

01:51.920 --> 01:53.759
You need to make the most of your time.

01:53.759 --> 01:54.840
Why participate in this competition

01:54.840 --> 01:56.430
where you just play with toys?

01:56.430 --> 01:57.789
Focus on improving your grades,

01:57.789 --> 01:59.229
getting into a good college,

01:59.229 --> 02:01.690
and finding a good job—
that's what matters.

02:15.750 --> 02:16.840
This isn't a toy.

02:17.870 --> 02:19.930
It's an architectural design model.

02:21.180 --> 02:24.190
[Episode 21:
A Dream I Never Dared to Have Before]

02:27.880 --> 02:29.590
[Investigation Report]
[Wang Qiang, the Missing Worker]

02:30.190 --> 02:31.790
This is that missing worker?

02:32.910 --> 02:34.110
He ran off to Nanyang.

02:38.630 --> 02:40.430
So you had news all along.

02:41.280 --> 02:41.960
Cheng.

02:43.190 --> 02:45.280
It's not that
I wouldn't let you investigate.

02:45.280 --> 02:47.590
I know there's something fishy about this.

02:47.590 --> 02:48.870
But Nanyang is too chaotic.

02:48.870 --> 02:49.800
The waters are too deep there.

02:49.800 --> 02:51.660
I didn't dare let you look into it.

02:53.470 --> 02:54.200
But you know,

02:55.470 --> 02:56.329
I won't give up.

02:56.430 --> 02:56.840
Right.

02:57.150 --> 02:57.680
I know.

02:59.030 --> 03:00.080
You look

03:00.360 --> 03:01.620
docile on the outside,

03:01.800 --> 03:03.560
but you're actually bold and driven,

03:03.560 --> 03:05.400
with a fire burning inside.

03:06.560 --> 03:07.310
If it weren't for

03:07.310 --> 03:08.470
that personality of yours,

03:08.470 --> 03:09.470
I wouldn't have invited you

03:09.470 --> 03:10.840
to join Zhiyuan in the first place.

03:10.840 --> 03:11.750
And even if I had,

03:11.750 --> 03:13.000
you wouldn't have given up

03:13.000 --> 03:14.030
your stable job in Jingcheng

03:14.030 --> 03:16.090
and come to Shengcheng to work for me.

03:17.470 --> 03:17.930
Senior,

03:19.280 --> 03:20.680
you really gave me

03:21.220 --> 03:22.750
an offer I couldn't refuse.

03:23.360 --> 03:25.360
If I had stayed in Jingcheng
following the routine,

03:25.360 --> 03:26.000
I wouldn't have been

03:26.000 --> 03:26.960
taking cases this soon.

03:26.960 --> 03:28.560
Alright, enough about that.

03:29.630 --> 03:30.890
Over the past few days,

03:31.090 --> 03:32.490
I've thought it through.

03:33.120 --> 03:33.800
I can't take advantage

03:33.800 --> 03:35.280
of your personality

03:35.800 --> 03:37.000
while trying to turn you into

03:37.000 --> 03:38.329
an obedient little boy.

03:40.430 --> 03:41.490
Handle this matter

03:41.840 --> 03:42.970
however you see fit.

03:43.310 --> 03:43.970
However...

03:44.430 --> 03:45.230
I understand.

03:45.520 --> 03:46.750
I'll definitely be careful.

03:46.750 --> 03:48.590
And I won't let it affect my other work.

03:48.590 --> 03:49.790
Don't worry, Senior.

03:55.280 --> 03:56.400
Dingsheng cake?

03:58.079 --> 03:59.280
I like the meaning of it—victory.

03:59.280 --> 03:59.960
We lawyers

03:59.960 --> 04:01.290
should eat more of this.

04:03.200 --> 04:04.660
Mr. Mao, this way, please.

04:08.800 --> 04:09.330
This way.

04:11.120 --> 04:12.360
I heard from many clients

04:12.360 --> 04:13.960
that for some small projects,

04:13.960 --> 04:14.680
you seem to be

04:14.680 --> 04:15.910
slacking off a bit now.

04:15.910 --> 04:16.750
That won't do.

04:20.750 --> 04:22.190
This is my uncle, Liu Yong.

04:22.190 --> 04:24.430
He's the General Manager
of Yuanhui Decoration.

04:24.430 --> 04:24.850
Alright.

04:24.850 --> 04:26.700
He came to Shengcheng in 1984

04:27.000 --> 04:28.560
and formed a renovation team,

04:28.560 --> 04:30.070
doing interior decoration.

04:30.070 --> 04:31.600
After winning the bid for the guesthouse,

04:31.600 --> 04:33.530
he started doing bigger projects.

04:34.270 --> 04:35.880
So for this bid,

04:35.950 --> 04:37.240
you're also participating

04:37.240 --> 04:38.390
under the name of your uncle's company?

04:38.390 --> 04:38.800
Yes.

04:39.159 --> 04:40.240
But after this,

04:40.360 --> 04:40.870
I plan to do it

04:40.870 --> 04:42.470
under my own company's name.

04:43.190 --> 04:45.020
This is my office area.

04:48.130 --> 04:50.100
Let's go in and take a look, shall we?

04:50.100 --> 04:50.500
Okay.

04:50.530 --> 04:51.310
Okay, this way.

04:51.310 --> 04:52.070
As for the design,

04:52.070 --> 04:52.870
this place...

04:53.600 --> 04:54.070
Yes, this...

04:54.070 --> 04:55.310
Yes, this is probably

04:55.750 --> 04:56.800
inside the private suite.

04:56.800 --> 04:57.360
Ms. Xia?

04:58.330 --> 04:59.810
M... Mr. Mao!

05:00.680 --> 05:01.270
Mr. Mao.

05:01.680 --> 05:02.810
It really is Mr. Mao.

05:04.430 --> 05:06.390
It seems I don't need to introduce you.

05:06.390 --> 05:07.040
Mr. Mao,

05:07.310 --> 05:08.480
these are the studio's

05:08.480 --> 05:09.360
current staff.

05:10.510 --> 05:11.510
This is Gong Yang.

05:11.680 --> 05:12.360
Hello, Mr. Mao.

05:12.360 --> 05:13.920
He's from the Oil Painting Department
at the Academy of Fine Arts.

05:13.920 --> 05:16.380
He's been with me
since the guesthouse days.

05:16.430 --> 05:17.480
This is Hou Qi.

05:17.870 --> 05:19.430
She used to work

05:19.430 --> 05:19.950
at the Jiangcheng Design Institute.

05:19.950 --> 05:20.950
She is his senior.

05:21.160 --> 05:21.630
After resigning,

05:21.630 --> 05:22.690
she came to join us.

05:23.240 --> 05:24.070
As for the rest,

05:24.070 --> 05:25.070
they are all

05:25.070 --> 05:26.310
students who haven't graduated yet.

05:26.310 --> 05:27.310
They're interning here

05:27.310 --> 05:28.480
to see if they're interested.

05:28.480 --> 05:29.950
Hello, Mr. Mao.

05:30.360 --> 05:31.360
Hello, everyone.

05:33.070 --> 05:34.270
Oh, right. Let's make way.

05:34.270 --> 05:34.870
Mr. Mao,

05:35.240 --> 05:36.360
this is some of our

05:36.390 --> 05:37.450
rough design work.

05:46.500 --> 05:47.940
It is indeed very rough.

05:48.510 --> 05:49.190
So, Mr. Mao,

05:49.190 --> 05:50.950
we are eager

05:50.950 --> 05:52.409
to receive your guidance.

05:53.000 --> 05:54.060
Alright, alright.

05:54.159 --> 05:55.480
Mr. Mao, let them discuss.

05:55.480 --> 05:56.390
Let's talk inside.

05:56.390 --> 05:56.750
Okay.

06:00.240 --> 06:01.750
Mr. Mao is so handsome.

06:01.870 --> 06:02.390
Mr. Mao,

06:02.680 --> 06:03.310
please have a seat.

06:03.310 --> 06:03.720
Okay.

06:18.630 --> 06:19.300
Have some tea.

06:19.300 --> 06:19.900
Thank you.

06:24.430 --> 06:25.720
On the way here,

06:25.950 --> 06:28.950
you made me look at
those construction sites on purpose.

06:28.950 --> 06:30.040
You said this place

06:30.060 --> 06:32.120
is full of opportunities and dreams.

06:32.630 --> 06:34.360
But have you thought about one thing?

06:34.360 --> 06:36.070
It is also full of

06:36.950 --> 06:38.680
helplessness and reality.

06:39.390 --> 06:41.630
You have talent and luck.

06:42.310 --> 06:44.370
But what about those people outside?

06:44.870 --> 06:46.270
Do they have your talent

06:46.270 --> 06:47.400
and opportunities?

06:48.040 --> 06:48.680
I admit

06:49.480 --> 06:51.070
that being able to
get to where I am today

06:51.070 --> 06:52.800
makes me one in a million lucky.

06:53.870 --> 06:54.750
But this doesn't conflict with

06:54.750 --> 06:56.010
my original intention

06:56.070 --> 06:57.470
of starting this studio.

06:57.480 --> 06:58.740
I'm not boasting about

06:58.870 --> 07:00.750
being responsible for anyone's future.

07:00.750 --> 07:02.120
How far they can go in the future

07:02.120 --> 07:03.450
depends on themselves.

07:04.240 --> 07:05.950
I just hope this studio

07:06.630 --> 07:08.270
can become their opportunity

07:08.270 --> 07:08.950
and luck.

07:10.040 --> 07:11.070
In that case,

07:12.750 --> 07:14.080
my trip won't be in vain.

07:15.040 --> 07:17.240
That's what you called "not boasting"?

07:17.400 --> 07:19.520
Since you went to my house,

07:20.190 --> 07:22.680
you've been talking big the whole time.

07:23.510 --> 07:24.270
But you still

07:24.270 --> 07:25.800
came to Shengcheng with me.

07:25.960 --> 07:27.490
Even if you just take a look,

07:27.720 --> 07:28.750
I'm already very grateful.

07:28.750 --> 07:31.000
I'm here for Haihua Hotel.

07:31.270 --> 07:33.920
I designed the proposal for Haihua Hotel.

07:34.040 --> 07:35.500
I have to take responsibility

07:35.500 --> 07:36.560
for my own project.

07:36.560 --> 07:38.890
I can't let you make changes
as you please.

07:41.960 --> 07:43.230
Tell me your ideas.

07:43.510 --> 07:44.600
I'm all ears.

07:45.480 --> 07:46.280
Just a moment.

07:59.830 --> 08:01.960
We've visited the construction site.

08:02.070 --> 08:03.430
The hotel's main structure

08:03.430 --> 08:04.900
is basically complete

08:05.240 --> 08:07.240
and is just waiting for decoration.

08:07.270 --> 08:08.160
I've also reviewed the proposal

08:08.160 --> 08:09.420
you provided earlier.

08:09.510 --> 08:11.310
The sail-style main building

08:11.390 --> 08:13.040
and the garden-style landscape.

08:13.040 --> 08:14.390
The time Dongfeng Holdings gave us

08:14.390 --> 08:15.720
is actually very short.

08:15.720 --> 08:16.680
So I plan to

08:16.750 --> 08:18.680
just make adjustments

08:18.680 --> 08:20.000
to the decoration's color scheme

08:20.000 --> 08:21.310
to make the hotel's style

08:21.310 --> 08:23.390
look more comfortable and casual

08:23.680 --> 08:25.080
and less business-like.

08:25.160 --> 08:26.160
What do you think?

08:28.870 --> 08:29.950
It seems you've reviewed

08:29.950 --> 08:31.600
quite a few domestic and international

08:31.600 --> 08:33.000
hotel decoration cases.

08:34.840 --> 08:36.970
That... that is quite a good attitude.

08:38.549 --> 08:39.870
You mean...

08:42.320 --> 08:44.380
Just draw it according to your ideas.

08:45.270 --> 08:47.240
Between the design and execution,

08:47.240 --> 08:48.040
there is a gap.

08:48.790 --> 08:50.990
If there's anything
that can't be realized,

08:50.990 --> 08:52.700
I'll remind you in time.

08:54.080 --> 08:56.140
Then about you joining the studio...

08:57.360 --> 08:58.690
We'll discuss it later.

09:02.910 --> 09:04.200
The factory guy

09:04.200 --> 09:04.670
was just about to

09:04.670 --> 09:06.000
hit me with his shovel.

09:06.120 --> 09:07.840
I blocked it like this.

09:07.870 --> 09:08.750
Guess what happened?

09:08.750 --> 09:10.150
-What happened?
-What happened?

09:10.150 --> 09:10.720
Then I...

09:10.720 --> 09:12.720
Your legs nearly gave out from fear!

09:12.730 --> 09:14.000
No, they didn't!

09:18.270 --> 09:19.440
Right, exactly.

09:19.750 --> 09:22.080
They nearly gave out from fear
on the site!

09:22.340 --> 09:23.000
You two...

09:23.270 --> 09:25.020
You really showed up at the wrong time.

09:25.020 --> 09:26.840
You didn't let me brag a bit longer.

09:26.840 --> 09:28.840
I hadn't gotten to the best part yet.

09:29.360 --> 09:31.120
You think they actually believe you?

09:31.120 --> 09:32.630
The real hero of that day

09:32.750 --> 09:33.670
was San.

09:34.360 --> 09:35.550
I made one phone call,

09:35.550 --> 09:37.600
and he came to help without hesitation.

09:37.600 --> 09:38.800
That's true loyalty.

09:39.240 --> 09:41.220
San, you didn't just come to our rescue,

09:41.220 --> 09:43.080
you even personally brought us
extra dishes.

09:43.080 --> 09:44.480
I run a restaurant, after all.

09:44.480 --> 09:45.750
Cooking a few extra dishes
to bring over...

09:45.750 --> 09:46.550
is no trouble.

09:47.670 --> 09:48.400
I have to say,

09:48.960 --> 09:50.270
when I was a seaman,

09:50.390 --> 09:51.150
I thought sailing to Nanyang

09:51.150 --> 09:52.320
was dangerous enough.

09:52.320 --> 09:52.910
I didn't expect that

09:52.910 --> 09:54.000
doing business in building materials

09:54.000 --> 09:55.240
would be this dangerous too.

09:55.240 --> 09:57.040
There are risks in any business.

09:57.270 --> 09:58.480
Zhenzhu, Wei,

09:58.870 --> 10:00.630
you two need to be more careful
in the future.

10:00.630 --> 10:02.630
Don't go investigating everything
by yourselves.

10:02.630 --> 10:03.870
We're a "tuandui."

10:04.000 --> 10:06.000
There's no shame in asking for help.

10:07.720 --> 10:08.650
It means "team."

10:09.840 --> 10:10.870
Anyway,

10:11.030 --> 10:12.890
we really need to thank San again.

10:13.080 --> 10:13.960
If you ever

10:14.000 --> 10:15.000
need any help in the future,

10:15.000 --> 10:16.400
I won't hesitate to help.

10:17.200 --> 10:19.530
Why don't you two just swear brotherhood?

10:19.840 --> 10:20.870
I think that's a great idea.

10:20.870 --> 10:21.910
Swear brotherhood.

10:21.910 --> 10:22.390
Let's have a toast.

10:22.390 --> 10:23.080
Alright, let's drink to that.

10:23.080 --> 10:24.150
Cheers.

10:24.390 --> 10:25.150
Welcome, San,

10:25.150 --> 10:26.270
to our team.

10:26.440 --> 10:26.840
Great.

10:26.870 --> 10:28.550
Welcome!

10:32.510 --> 10:33.630
When are you two

10:33.910 --> 10:35.910
going to get your marriage license?

10:38.600 --> 10:40.320
We've both been busy lately.

10:40.600 --> 10:43.000
After the bidding
for Haihua Hotel is over,

10:43.000 --> 10:44.400
we'll go get registered.

10:45.150 --> 10:45.750
By the way,

10:45.960 --> 10:47.600
once we win the bid for the hotel,

10:47.600 --> 10:49.360
our Happy Life Materials

10:49.360 --> 10:51.150
will get another big deal, right?

10:51.150 --> 10:52.080
Not bad, Wei.

10:52.320 --> 10:53.910
All you think about now is big deals.

10:53.910 --> 10:55.360
Of course.

10:55.550 --> 10:57.390
Big deals! Big deals!

11:02.390 --> 11:03.120
Alright then,

11:03.120 --> 11:03.720
Young Master,

11:03.720 --> 11:04.840
I'll get going then.

11:04.840 --> 11:06.000
I'll report back if there's any news.

11:06.000 --> 11:06.330
Okay.

11:09.150 --> 11:11.810
Second Young Master,
you're in Shengcheng too?

11:13.600 --> 11:15.080
What is that loser doing here?

11:15.080 --> 11:15.840
Why didn't you tell me

11:15.840 --> 11:16.870
to arrange a reception?

11:16.870 --> 11:17.400
Mr. Meng.

11:17.790 --> 11:19.360
Daddy asked me to come on short notice

11:19.360 --> 11:20.320
to handle some matters.

11:20.320 --> 11:21.630
I'll definitely let you know
in advance next time.

11:21.630 --> 11:22.440
Okay, okay.

11:26.960 --> 11:27.960
I'm leaving then.

11:32.240 --> 11:32.970
Big Brother.

11:35.550 --> 11:36.150
By the way,

11:38.360 --> 11:39.620
Daddy told me to ask you

11:39.630 --> 11:43.030
about the progress
of the shoe and clothing factory project.

11:43.030 --> 11:43.870
I

11:44.510 --> 11:46.310
will speak to the old man myself.

11:47.040 --> 11:48.900
I don't need you to be a messenger.

11:51.840 --> 11:52.240
Okay.

11:54.270 --> 11:55.790
I have an appointment,

11:56.150 --> 11:57.080
so I'll go in now.

11:57.120 --> 11:58.920
I'll come find you when I'm done.

11:59.630 --> 12:01.290
Take care. I won't see you out.

12:02.870 --> 12:03.510
Loser.

12:04.870 --> 12:05.550
Building a factory

12:05.550 --> 12:06.480
is not that easy.

12:07.030 --> 12:08.120
Why did the old man

12:08.200 --> 12:08.840
send him here?

12:08.840 --> 12:09.500
To scare me?

12:09.720 --> 12:10.600
I don't know.

12:11.080 --> 12:11.810
Have someone

12:11.840 --> 12:13.030
keep a close eye on the group.

12:13.030 --> 12:13.360
Okay.

12:14.840 --> 12:17.120
The shoe and clothing factory
takes too long to make a profit.

12:17.120 --> 12:19.000
We must find a project

12:19.080 --> 12:19.910
that yields results

12:19.910 --> 12:20.870
in the short term.

12:20.870 --> 12:22.670
Even a small project would work.

12:23.150 --> 12:24.360
Didn't Mr. Tang of Meihua

12:24.360 --> 12:26.080
invest in a

12:26.120 --> 12:27.400
five-star hotel in Shengcheng?

12:27.400 --> 12:28.280
Is there any opportunity for cooperation?

12:28.280 --> 12:29.520
Mr. Tang invested in

12:29.550 --> 12:30.390
Haihua Hotel.

12:30.510 --> 12:32.030
The exterior is finished,

12:32.030 --> 12:33.510
but the interior isn't.

12:34.550 --> 12:35.320
I remember now.

12:35.320 --> 12:36.870
Last time, Liu Tianquan

12:37.030 --> 12:38.600
bid for that guesthouse

12:38.870 --> 12:40.200
to pave the way for this.

12:41.870 --> 12:43.720
He wanted to do the...

12:43.720 --> 12:45.380
decoration for Haihua Hotel.

12:46.890 --> 12:47.840
But you transferred him

12:47.840 --> 12:49.030
to Gangdao.

12:49.200 --> 12:50.960
Now we don't know the situation.

12:50.960 --> 12:53.220
That damn loser actually has foresight.

12:54.550 --> 12:55.550
Arrange a meeting with the person

12:55.550 --> 12:56.270
in charge of Chengrong Tianchen.

12:56.270 --> 12:56.550
Okay.

12:56.550 --> 12:56.960
Also,

12:57.240 --> 12:58.150
make an appointment

12:58.150 --> 12:58.950
with Mr. Tang.

12:58.960 --> 12:59.620
No problem.

13:02.910 --> 13:04.550
If you hadn't stopped them just now,

13:04.550 --> 13:05.480
I think San

13:05.480 --> 13:07.810
would have sworn brotherhood with Zhenzhu.

13:07.810 --> 13:08.720
I wonder when those two

13:08.720 --> 13:09.840
will finally

13:09.840 --> 13:10.910
confess their feelings.

13:10.910 --> 13:12.310
I think it's kinda tough.

13:12.390 --> 13:13.000
They probably

13:13.000 --> 13:13.790
need something

13:13.790 --> 13:14.850
to give them a push.

13:15.480 --> 13:16.600
Yeah. No rush.

13:16.970 --> 13:18.330
That day will come,

13:18.360 --> 13:19.620
and so will that event.

13:21.270 --> 13:22.130
Let me quiz you.

13:22.750 --> 13:24.550
What event brought us together?

13:24.840 --> 13:25.870
I'm not like San.

13:26.720 --> 13:28.480
From the first time I saw you,

13:29.000 --> 13:30.260
I knew you were the one.

13:30.500 --> 13:31.670
The Xia Xiaolan from Dahe Village,

13:31.670 --> 13:33.120
who was chased by a crowd,

13:33.670 --> 13:34.800
has been living here

13:36.550 --> 13:37.600
ever since.

13:39.970 --> 13:40.610
Really?

13:41.480 --> 13:42.280
Let me listen.

13:42.960 --> 13:44.290
What am I doing in there?

13:46.550 --> 13:48.120
She seems to be saying

13:48.600 --> 13:50.930
that she wants to stay here
for a lifetime.

13:51.960 --> 13:53.120
Did I hear that right?

13:53.120 --> 13:53.720
Yes.

13:54.150 --> 13:55.010
For a lifetime.

14:02.390 --> 14:03.910
I always feel like this thing

14:03.910 --> 14:05.040
is important to you,

14:05.200 --> 14:06.400
so I bought it for you.

14:07.840 --> 14:09.150
It feels like fate.

14:10.270 --> 14:11.320
This alarm clock

14:11.870 --> 14:13.320
came back to me after all.

14:14.670 --> 14:16.200
It's like it's reminding me

14:17.400 --> 14:19.800
that I can't escape the destiny
of leaving.

14:20.630 --> 14:21.750
Did you think

14:21.870 --> 14:23.080
buying a clock was bad luck

14:23.080 --> 14:24.320
the other day we were out?

14:24.320 --> 14:25.920
Is that why you didn't buy it?

14:26.120 --> 14:26.980
How about this?

14:27.600 --> 14:28.530
Give me one yuan.

14:31.080 --> 14:31.790
When I was young,

14:31.790 --> 14:33.050
my grandmother told me

14:33.150 --> 14:34.390
that if I gave her one yuan,

14:34.390 --> 14:35.270
it would be as if

14:35.270 --> 14:36.150
I had just bought it from her.

14:36.150 --> 14:37.280
Then all the bad luck

14:37.510 --> 14:38.710
would be washed away.

14:47.510 --> 14:48.170
Zhou Cheng.

14:49.120 --> 14:49.720
Thank you.

14:52.480 --> 14:53.150
I don't know

14:54.080 --> 14:55.270
how long my lifetime here

14:55.270 --> 14:56.120
really is.

14:57.240 --> 14:59.390
I just hope it will be long enough.

15:00.240 --> 15:01.080
Long enough.

15:07.380 --> 15:08.170
This area—

15:08.200 --> 15:09.600
how can we block it?

15:17.790 --> 15:18.650
Don't you think

15:18.960 --> 15:20.630
changing Mr. Mao's plan

15:20.630 --> 15:21.360
right in front of him

15:21.360 --> 15:23.390
is a bit presumptuous of us?

15:23.670 --> 15:24.480
I don't know.

15:24.670 --> 15:26.630
If Ms. Xia says it's fine, it's fine.

15:26.630 --> 15:27.240
Besides,

15:27.480 --> 15:28.480
we aren't changing much.

15:28.480 --> 15:29.440
If you speak any louder,

15:29.440 --> 15:30.870
I won't be able to hear you.

15:30.870 --> 15:32.000
I'm hard of hearing.

15:32.080 --> 15:32.510
Mr. Mao.

15:32.510 --> 15:33.710
Mr. Mao, we're sorry.

15:33.840 --> 15:35.440
What's there to be sorry for?

15:35.920 --> 15:37.780
Change whatever needs changing.

15:38.000 --> 15:39.320
Your Ms. Xia has already

15:39.320 --> 15:40.720
paid my consulting fee anyway.

15:40.720 --> 15:42.120
I'm not losing anything.

15:42.600 --> 15:44.260
Let's take a break, everyone.

15:44.750 --> 15:46.200
The deadline for this plan is tight.

15:46.200 --> 15:47.670
Thank you for your hard work
these past few days.

15:47.670 --> 15:49.030
Once the results are out,

15:49.030 --> 15:50.480
whether we win the bid or not,

15:50.480 --> 15:51.790
everyone gets a bonus.

15:52.390 --> 15:54.030
We'll definitely win!

15:54.240 --> 15:55.770
If we win, double the bonus!

15:58.480 --> 15:59.270
Okay!

15:59.510 --> 16:00.040
Let's go.

16:01.030 --> 16:02.750
Here, help yourselves.

16:02.840 --> 16:03.200
Okay.

16:04.000 --> 16:04.750
Mr. Mao,

16:05.080 --> 16:07.000
regarding the modifications to the plan,

16:07.000 --> 16:09.330
I have an idea
I'd like to discuss with you.

16:09.490 --> 16:13.530
[Gangdao]

16:10.320 --> 16:11.150
Shengcheng

16:11.360 --> 16:13.160
doesn't have a lounge this nice.

16:13.170 --> 16:15.500
Unlike me, you don't come back every week.

16:15.630 --> 16:17.510
It's been a while since you really
enjoyed yourself, hasn't it?

16:17.510 --> 16:18.710
There'll be one soon.

16:18.840 --> 16:20.390
Shengcheng is developing so fast.

16:20.390 --> 16:22.250
Everyone wants a slice of the pie.

16:24.440 --> 16:25.030
Zhaohui,

16:25.680 --> 16:26.810
I know what you mean.

16:27.600 --> 16:29.260
It's not that I won't help you.

16:29.630 --> 16:31.790
The Haihua matter isn't that simple.

16:32.600 --> 16:33.530
Besides Meihua,

16:33.720 --> 16:35.390
Haihua has 3 other shareholders.

16:35.390 --> 16:37.250
One of them is Dongfeng Holdings.

16:37.390 --> 16:38.480
Mainland capital—

16:38.630 --> 16:39.390
as you know—

16:40.270 --> 16:41.550
is now competing fiercely

16:41.550 --> 16:42.750
with us.

16:44.390 --> 16:45.150
Is there anything you want

16:45.150 --> 16:46.550
that you can't get, Tang?

16:47.120 --> 16:48.390
You're luckier than I am.

16:48.390 --> 16:49.270
You know my situation at home,

16:49.270 --> 16:50.080
don't you?

16:50.870 --> 16:51.870
If you help me,

16:52.440 --> 16:53.240
in the future,

16:53.320 --> 16:54.790
when I have more say,

16:55.200 --> 16:56.800
I'll naturally help you too.

16:57.840 --> 16:58.720
Then you

16:58.720 --> 16:59.850
need to move faster.

17:00.440 --> 17:02.770
The shareholders' meeting is on the 20th.

17:03.150 --> 17:04.589
I've reviewed your plan.

17:05.000 --> 17:06.329
It was actually not bad.

17:07.310 --> 17:08.310
But rumor has it

17:08.480 --> 17:10.410
Dongfeng is modifying their plan.

17:10.720 --> 17:11.480
So you guys

17:11.880 --> 17:14.010
might want to optimize yours further.

17:14.069 --> 17:14.510
Hua.

17:17.270 --> 17:18.109
As you know,

17:18.550 --> 17:20.280
I'm a straightforward person.

17:20.510 --> 17:21.550
I just want to know

17:21.880 --> 17:22.640
what expectations the shareholders

17:22.640 --> 17:23.880
have for the hotel.

17:24.160 --> 17:25.890
How should the plan be changed?

17:26.200 --> 17:26.960
This is our company's

17:26.960 --> 17:27.890
designer, Meng.

17:27.960 --> 17:29.000
I brought him here today.

17:29.000 --> 17:30.460
We hope for your guidance.

17:32.680 --> 17:33.340
Bartender.

17:39.830 --> 17:41.360
You're asking a favor of me,

17:41.590 --> 17:43.590
yet you picked such a strong liquor.

17:44.000 --> 17:45.070
If I had gone easy,

17:45.400 --> 17:47.130
would you have agreed to see me?

17:48.920 --> 17:50.320
I like your personality.

17:51.880 --> 17:52.880
I'll be straight.

17:53.830 --> 17:54.640
Reviewing the proposals

17:54.640 --> 17:56.240
is just a formality.

17:56.640 --> 17:58.000
Your odds are good.

17:59.070 --> 18:00.000
Dongfeng found

18:00.000 --> 18:01.960
a so-called "master" in the mainland.

18:01.960 --> 18:02.960
But their plan

18:03.640 --> 18:05.590
is flawed from the start.

18:10.270 --> 18:10.830
Mr. Mao,

18:11.110 --> 18:12.000
are you going with me

18:12.000 --> 18:13.130
to the bid tomorrow?

18:13.350 --> 18:14.150
I'm not going.

18:14.510 --> 18:15.770
I'm just a consultant.

18:16.230 --> 18:17.510
This is your own

18:17.510 --> 18:18.350
revised plan.

18:19.010 --> 18:20.450
The work I promised you

18:20.480 --> 18:22.550
is done as of today.

18:23.240 --> 18:25.500
I'm going back to the guesthouse to rest.

18:25.830 --> 18:26.200
Okay.

18:26.880 --> 18:28.210
Ge Jian, see Mr. Mao out.

18:38.240 --> 18:39.310
Mr. Mao still won't

18:39.310 --> 18:40.240
join the studio?

18:42.590 --> 18:44.240
Mr. Mao has been working
in Hangcheng Design Institute

18:44.240 --> 18:44.960
for so many years.

18:44.960 --> 18:46.110
And he's retiring soon.

18:46.110 --> 18:47.960
It's understandable
he doesn't want the hassle.

18:47.960 --> 18:49.240
It's a pity, though.

18:49.590 --> 18:50.680
He seems to have

18:50.680 --> 18:51.440
a bad temper,

18:51.480 --> 18:51.790
but

18:52.160 --> 18:53.640
he points out

18:53.640 --> 18:55.100
the key issues every time.

18:57.000 --> 18:59.730
Thank you all for your hard work
during this time.

19:00.000 --> 19:00.880
Take

19:01.070 --> 19:02.270
the next two days off.

19:03.270 --> 19:05.530
-Thank you, Ms. Xia!
-Thank you, Ms. Xia!

19:07.920 --> 19:08.920
Goodbye, Ms. Xia.

19:08.920 --> 19:09.450
Goodbye.

19:09.720 --> 19:10.250
Goodbye.

19:10.720 --> 19:11.400
President Xia,

19:11.400 --> 19:12.530
you're not leaving?

19:12.680 --> 19:13.720
If you need anything,

19:13.720 --> 19:14.790
I can stay and help...

19:14.790 --> 19:15.880
No need.

19:15.960 --> 19:16.790
Goodbye, Ms. Xia!

19:16.790 --> 19:17.790
Goodbye, Ms. Xia!

19:18.030 --> 19:18.560
Bye-bye.

19:20.830 --> 19:22.230
The bidding is tomorrow.

19:22.400 --> 19:24.030
You need to familiarize yourself
with the plan, right?

19:24.030 --> 19:24.790
Yes.

19:24.960 --> 19:26.360
I need to go over it again.

19:26.440 --> 19:26.880
Okay.

19:27.620 --> 19:28.860
You go over the plan,

19:29.000 --> 19:30.460
and I'll go over the files.

19:30.680 --> 19:31.610
If we are hungry,

19:31.720 --> 19:32.920
there's roast goose.

19:33.000 --> 19:34.000
And if we're thirsty,

19:34.000 --> 19:34.930
there are Cokes.

19:36.160 --> 19:37.130
Well, Ms. Xia?

19:37.680 --> 19:38.680
Are you satisfied

19:38.830 --> 19:40.160
with this arrangement?

19:40.510 --> 19:41.440
Very satisfied.

19:42.680 --> 19:43.880
If you're satisfied,

19:44.590 --> 19:45.650
after the bidding,

19:45.830 --> 19:46.880
can you give me

19:47.300 --> 19:49.030
my "employment certificate"?

19:51.880 --> 19:52.540
Zhou Cheng,

19:53.030 --> 19:54.270
I make you wait every time.

19:54.270 --> 19:54.870
I promise,

19:55.160 --> 19:56.070
never again.

19:59.070 --> 19:59.440
Okay.

20:07.310 --> 20:08.170
I like this one.

20:10.400 --> 20:11.460
Morning, Mr. Tang.

20:11.550 --> 20:12.280
You're here.

20:12.720 --> 20:13.320
You may go.

20:14.750 --> 20:15.880
That Manager Huo...

20:16.480 --> 20:18.350
I tried to arrange a meeting
with him several times.

20:18.350 --> 20:20.480
He's so difficult to get an appointment
with. So hard to deal with.

20:20.480 --> 20:22.720
I'd like to see him for myself today.

20:28.590 --> 20:29.190
He's here.

20:29.400 --> 20:30.400
See for yourself.

20:30.510 --> 20:31.920
Exactly the type I hate.

20:40.030 --> 20:40.560
Morning,

20:40.790 --> 20:41.520
Manager Huo.

20:41.920 --> 20:42.240
Morning.

20:42.240 --> 20:43.030
Which design company

20:43.030 --> 20:44.090
did Dongfeng hire?

20:44.160 --> 20:44.960
And their proposal—

20:44.960 --> 20:46.090
do you know about it?

20:46.240 --> 20:46.830
It's the Yuanhui

20:46.830 --> 20:47.590
that bid against us

20:47.590 --> 20:49.240
for this guesthouse project last time.

20:49.240 --> 20:49.830
Yuanhui?

20:50.920 --> 20:51.550
Such an important matter—

20:51.550 --> 20:52.810
why didn't you tell me?

20:53.270 --> 20:54.680
You didn't ask me.

20:57.420 --> 20:59.440
Do you think my company
is too small for you

20:59.440 --> 21:00.830
and that you want to work
for Liu Tianquan instead?

21:00.830 --> 21:01.480
No, no.

21:04.000 --> 21:04.640
Mr. Du,

21:05.440 --> 21:06.480
is this Yuanhui

21:07.030 --> 21:08.430
really that impressive?

21:09.070 --> 21:10.400
I heard this guesthouse

21:10.440 --> 21:12.000
went with their design.

21:12.480 --> 21:14.480
It looks like nothing special to me.

21:14.590 --> 21:15.920
They can't compare with

21:16.230 --> 21:17.360
Gangdao designers.

21:18.790 --> 21:19.480
Mr. Tang,

21:19.830 --> 21:20.750
don't underestimate

21:20.750 --> 21:21.410
this woman.

21:28.590 --> 21:29.160
Sorry.

21:29.270 --> 21:30.530
I placed them wrongly.

21:31.700 --> 21:33.250
[Yuanhui Decoration Co., Ltd.]

21:54.400 --> 21:56.860
We really have a connection
with this place.

21:56.960 --> 21:57.750
Our first project

21:57.750 --> 21:58.610
was right here.

21:58.960 --> 21:59.750
Now we're back here

21:59.750 --> 22:01.280
for an even bigger project.

22:02.030 --> 22:03.230
I was nervous before.

22:03.510 --> 22:04.110
But seeing this place,

22:04.110 --> 22:05.570
I'm not nervous at all now.

22:06.640 --> 22:07.440
I also believe

22:07.590 --> 22:09.390
this will be a lucky place for us.

22:10.030 --> 22:10.560
Let's go.

22:16.750 --> 22:17.210
Ms. Xia.

22:30.160 --> 22:30.620
Ms. Xia,

22:30.880 --> 22:31.960
what a coincidence.

22:31.960 --> 22:33.620
But we're competitors today.

22:33.880 --> 22:35.080
I won't go easy on you.

22:35.450 --> 22:36.920
Then I must thank you, Mr. Du,

22:36.920 --> 22:38.030
for putting in all your effort.

22:38.030 --> 22:38.830
It will make Yuanhui's victory

22:38.830 --> 22:39.960
even more valuable.

22:41.880 --> 22:46.030
[We look forward to your return
at Shengcheng Guesthouse]

22:43.070 --> 22:44.470
Thank you all for coming.

22:45.030 --> 22:45.960
Haihua Hotel

22:46.160 --> 22:48.620
is the first five-star hotel
in Shengcheng.

22:48.680 --> 22:49.400
In the future,

22:49.400 --> 22:50.640
it will also become

22:50.640 --> 22:51.970
a landmark of this city.

22:52.480 --> 22:53.790
And it will serve as a calling card

22:53.790 --> 22:55.510
for the city to the outside world.

22:55.510 --> 22:57.160
It is also a model of cooperation

22:57.160 --> 22:58.790
between state-owned capital
and Gangcheng capital.

22:58.790 --> 22:59.790
Its importance

22:59.960 --> 23:01.020
speaks for itself.

23:02.720 --> 23:03.580
I hope everyone

23:04.350 --> 23:06.610
can introduce your proposals in detail,

23:07.140 --> 23:08.800
so that the investors present

23:09.000 --> 23:10.530
and the expert review panel

23:11.020 --> 23:11.960
can discuss,

23:12.270 --> 23:12.790
vote,

23:13.200 --> 23:15.260
and select the final winning bidder.

23:15.310 --> 23:15.750
Mr. Du,

23:16.320 --> 23:17.780
would you like to go first?

23:17.830 --> 23:18.680
Our company

23:18.680 --> 23:20.410
has always been very concerned

23:20.720 --> 23:22.880
with Shengcheng's economic development,

23:22.880 --> 23:25.010
and we have always participated in it.

23:26.200 --> 23:27.750
This is the design proposal

23:27.750 --> 23:29.070
we made for Haihua Hotel.

23:29.070 --> 23:31.000
Please take a look, shareholders.

23:32.880 --> 23:34.590
Providing a result worth 30 million

23:34.590 --> 23:36.320
with a quotation of 25 million—

23:36.830 --> 23:38.890
that's the sincerity of our company.

23:42.270 --> 23:43.680
Dongfeng found

23:43.960 --> 23:45.400
a so-called "master" in the mainland.

23:45.400 --> 23:46.550
But their plan

23:46.920 --> 23:49.070
is flawed from the start.

23:50.400 --> 23:52.530
For a five-star international hotel,

23:52.720 --> 23:53.310
Dongfeng

23:53.640 --> 23:54.920
is still using the mindset of decorating

23:54.920 --> 23:56.180
guesthouses and inns.

23:56.310 --> 23:57.840
With a budget of 16 million,

23:57.920 --> 23:59.000
how could those shareholders

23:59.000 --> 24:00.350
possibly be impressed?

24:02.480 --> 24:03.210
Manager Huo,

24:03.640 --> 24:04.640
what do you think?

24:07.680 --> 24:09.070
I think when it comes to design,

24:09.070 --> 24:10.640
it needs to be brought to the table

24:10.640 --> 24:11.550
for discussion.

24:11.550 --> 24:12.480
Don't you agree?

24:14.830 --> 24:16.830
Tianchen's proposal is quite good.

24:18.240 --> 24:19.680
Based on these standards,

24:19.680 --> 24:22.410
Tianchen is offering
significant concessions.

24:22.440 --> 24:23.240
I think so too.

24:23.880 --> 24:24.210
Okay.

24:24.790 --> 24:28.120
Let's also look at the proposals
from Dongfeng and Yuanhui.

24:39.160 --> 24:39.760
Thank you.

24:43.270 --> 24:44.470
This is our proposal.

24:44.720 --> 24:46.310
If anyone has any questions,

24:46.310 --> 24:47.350
please feel free to ask our designer

24:47.350 --> 24:48.210
to answer them.

24:49.240 --> 24:50.840
This is the revised proposal

24:51.240 --> 24:53.110
by our Yuanhui Decoration

24:53.310 --> 24:55.370
based on the work of Mr. Mao Kangshan.

24:55.680 --> 24:56.240
Alright.

24:56.710 --> 24:57.860
Let me see

24:58.270 --> 24:59.240
this 16 million—

24:59.990 --> 25:01.420
[Haihua Hotel: 30 Million Renovation Plan
and Cost Breakdown]

25:03.200 --> 25:04.330
Why is it 30 million?

25:05.400 --> 25:06.330
That's correct.

25:06.590 --> 25:08.350
Yuanhui's revised proposal

25:08.640 --> 25:09.840
is indeed 30 million.

25:14.830 --> 25:15.310
What?

25:15.550 --> 25:16.550
Within 10 days,

25:16.550 --> 25:18.350
you are going to make two proposals?

25:18.350 --> 25:20.200
Yuanhui will provide the proposal

25:20.200 --> 25:21.730
with a budget of 16 million.

25:22.000 --> 25:23.080
In addition to that,

25:23.080 --> 25:24.720
we are also providing an extra proposal

25:24.720 --> 25:26.160
with a budget of 30 million.

25:26.160 --> 25:27.090
I'd like to know—

25:27.170 --> 25:28.970
why did you increase the budget?

25:29.000 --> 25:30.730
Sixteen million is quite a lot,

25:31.030 --> 25:31.790
but that's only

25:31.790 --> 25:33.120
for us ordinary people.

25:33.160 --> 25:33.960
To decorate

25:33.960 --> 25:35.350
a five-star hotel,

25:35.640 --> 25:36.820
it's not luxurious enough.

25:36.820 --> 25:39.030
We shouldn't forget the lifestyle
of hard work and plain living,

25:39.030 --> 25:40.680
but for the Shengcheng Special Zone,

25:40.680 --> 25:42.210
as a new window to the world,

25:42.440 --> 25:44.030
shouldn't we add some

25:44.030 --> 25:45.360
more brilliant colors?

25:45.590 --> 25:46.510
The shareholders in Gangdao

25:46.510 --> 25:48.350
rejecting your previous proposal

25:48.350 --> 25:48.880
may not be

25:49.280 --> 25:50.970
simply a matter

25:51.000 --> 25:52.440
of opposing Dongfeng Holdings.

25:52.440 --> 25:53.880
You mean...

25:54.750 --> 25:57.480
Huo Chenzhou
misunderstood their requirements?

25:57.480 --> 26:00.050
The people from Gangdao
don't want to save money,

26:00.050 --> 26:02.320
but rather a landmark

26:02.350 --> 26:04.150
with architectural influence?

26:04.400 --> 26:04.880
Yes.

26:05.240 --> 26:06.590
We are helping Dongfeng

26:06.920 --> 26:08.720
improve its chances of winning.

26:09.160 --> 26:10.070
Manager Huo,

26:10.790 --> 26:11.790
you can't just take

26:11.790 --> 26:13.990
Mr. Mao Kangshan's original proposal,

26:14.070 --> 26:15.160
double the price,

26:15.160 --> 26:16.820
and present it again, can you?

26:17.070 --> 26:18.270
Mr. Mao Kangshan

26:18.480 --> 26:19.480
is indeed the consultant

26:19.480 --> 26:21.400
for Yuanhui's decoration proposal.

26:21.400 --> 26:23.000
He has given us a lot of help,

26:23.310 --> 26:24.350
but this proposal

26:24.480 --> 26:25.810
has truly been revised.

26:28.070 --> 26:29.160
You can easily

26:29.680 --> 26:30.270
see the differences

26:30.270 --> 26:32.100
by comparing these two proposals.

26:32.100 --> 26:33.400
The European-style fountain

26:33.400 --> 26:34.790
in the center was removed

26:34.790 --> 26:37.520
and replaced with palm trees
and a swimming pool.

26:39.830 --> 26:40.750
The entrance,

26:41.310 --> 26:42.110
the atrium,

26:42.550 --> 26:43.280
and the roof—

26:43.790 --> 26:45.400
that's 3 swimming pools in total.

26:45.400 --> 26:47.460
It's more than just 3 swimming pools.

26:47.680 --> 26:48.410
Shengcheng—

26:48.440 --> 26:50.590
as a special zone
of the Reform and Opening-Up—

26:50.590 --> 26:52.240
companies like HSBC, Meihua,

26:52.240 --> 26:53.880
and Gangdao Investment

26:54.590 --> 26:55.480
were among the first

26:55.480 --> 26:57.210
foreign enterprises to enter.

26:57.310 --> 26:58.240
In the future,

26:58.240 --> 27:00.070
more foreign enterprises will come in.

27:00.070 --> 27:02.200
People from all over the world
will come to Shengcheng

27:02.200 --> 27:03.960
to do business through the special zone.

27:03.960 --> 27:06.070
Haihua Hotel is situated at the port,

27:06.440 --> 27:08.440
with an endless view of the sea.

27:09.160 --> 27:10.200
Such beautiful scenery—

27:10.200 --> 27:11.660
we can't just fence it off.

27:11.880 --> 27:13.550
Instead, we want our guests

27:14.030 --> 27:16.110
to have the ultimate experience.

27:17.880 --> 27:18.400
So,

27:18.750 --> 27:20.510
our biggest highlight this time

27:20.510 --> 27:22.510
is actually the infinity pool.

27:27.790 --> 27:28.520
Impossible.

27:29.680 --> 27:31.410
It's technically unfeasible.

27:31.590 --> 27:33.400
The renderings are just drawings.

27:33.400 --> 27:36.330
The main structure
of the hotel is already finished.

27:36.350 --> 27:37.640
Mr. Mao Kangshan

27:38.110 --> 27:40.640
is the designer
of the hotel's main structure.

27:40.640 --> 27:42.240
He thinks it can be modified.

27:42.440 --> 27:43.720
Regarding the technical aspects,

27:43.720 --> 27:45.320
we have already verified it.

27:50.070 --> 27:50.600
Mr. Tang,

27:50.720 --> 27:52.920
do you have any other proposals to show?

27:55.160 --> 27:56.360
The infinity pool...

27:57.330 --> 27:58.130
this concept,

27:58.270 --> 27:59.980
is something none of us have heard of.

27:59.980 --> 28:00.680
It's hard to imagine

28:00.680 --> 28:02.940
how difficult the construction will be.

28:03.110 --> 28:04.970
Even if it's technically feasible,

28:04.970 --> 28:06.730
the cost will be substantial.

28:06.960 --> 28:08.680
That means the investment
for decorating other parts

28:08.680 --> 28:10.030
of the hotel will decrease.

28:10.030 --> 28:11.350
To ensure the achievement

28:11.350 --> 28:12.400
of the decoration effect,

28:12.400 --> 28:13.800
can a budget of 30 million

28:13.960 --> 28:14.920
really suffice?

28:15.440 --> 28:16.970
So, Mr. Tang, are you saying

28:17.550 --> 28:19.260
we should increase the budget?

28:19.260 --> 28:21.030
Personally, I have no objection.

28:21.030 --> 28:22.350
However, from the perspective

28:22.350 --> 28:23.480
of other investors,

28:23.830 --> 28:25.680
maintaining the original budget

28:25.680 --> 28:26.810
is more reasonable.

28:28.830 --> 28:30.070
Tianchen's proposal is

28:30.070 --> 28:31.310
to use a budget of 25 million

28:31.310 --> 28:33.110
to achieve a 30-million effect,

28:33.480 --> 28:35.610
while we will use a budget of 30 million

28:36.000 --> 28:37.800
to achieve a 50-million effect.

28:38.790 --> 28:39.390
Mr. Tang,

28:39.680 --> 28:42.080
if you're concerned about funding issues,

28:42.720 --> 28:43.650
we'll handle it.

28:58.790 --> 29:00.830
After review by the bidding committee,

29:00.830 --> 29:02.110
the winning bidders are

29:02.110 --> 29:04.880
Dongfeng Holdings and Yuanhui Decoration.

29:05.920 --> 29:06.850
Starting today,

29:07.030 --> 29:07.960
the bid winner announcement

29:07.960 --> 29:10.090
will be publicly displayed for 7 days.

29:10.240 --> 29:11.960
If there are no objections
after the public display,

29:11.960 --> 29:12.830
the bidding committee

29:12.830 --> 29:14.350
will issue the winning bidders

29:14.350 --> 29:16.230
a formal letter of acceptance,

29:16.400 --> 29:18.000
and we'll sign the contract.

29:20.270 --> 29:20.840
Xiaolan,

29:21.510 --> 29:23.010
once the 30-million project is completed,

29:23.010 --> 29:24.480
Yuanhui gets a quarter of it.

29:24.480 --> 29:26.300
Yuanhui has really made it this time.

29:26.300 --> 29:27.960
We must do a good job this time.

29:28.030 --> 29:29.070
It's not just about making money,

29:29.070 --> 29:30.510
but also ensuring our reputation.

29:30.510 --> 29:31.790
With the experience

29:31.790 --> 29:33.240
of decorating a five-star hotel,

29:33.240 --> 29:34.240
Yuanhui will be confident

29:34.240 --> 29:34.830
to take on any project in the future.

29:34.830 --> 29:35.560
Don't worry.

29:35.750 --> 29:36.400
We definitely won't drop the ball

29:36.400 --> 29:37.860
on the construction side.

29:38.200 --> 29:39.160
This time, besides

29:39.160 --> 29:41.010
making a profit on the construction,

29:41.010 --> 29:42.070
most of the building materials

29:42.070 --> 29:43.640
can be supplied by our store.

29:43.640 --> 29:45.720
This way, Happy Life Materials' performance
for the second half of the year

29:45.720 --> 29:47.070
will be more or less sufficient.

29:47.070 --> 29:47.510
Uncle,

29:47.880 --> 29:49.410
do you know what this means?

29:49.440 --> 29:51.640
It means we'll make double the profit.

29:52.070 --> 29:53.720
Bai and Wei will make money too.

29:53.720 --> 29:55.180
Xiaolan, you're the best.

29:55.240 --> 29:56.240
You helped all of us

29:56.240 --> 29:57.100
make a killing.

29:58.240 --> 30:00.170
Ms. Xia, you're truly impressive.

30:03.590 --> 30:04.350
This time,

30:04.790 --> 30:06.120
we lost fair and square.

30:06.550 --> 30:07.440
How did you come up with

30:07.440 --> 30:08.570
that infinity pool?

30:08.960 --> 30:10.160
When I saw the design,

30:10.160 --> 30:11.080
I thought of

30:11.110 --> 30:12.970
many beautiful girls in bikinis.

30:15.480 --> 30:16.400
I mean,

30:16.720 --> 30:17.790
this infinity pool

30:17.790 --> 30:18.750
will definitely attract many

30:18.750 --> 30:20.000
tourists to Shengcheng

30:20.000 --> 30:21.440
and Haihua Hotel.

30:23.270 --> 30:24.330
Let's go, Xiaolan.

30:26.480 --> 30:27.000
Bye.

30:30.240 --> 30:31.240
See you next time.

30:37.640 --> 30:38.110
Boss.

30:41.400 --> 30:42.570
That Gangdao merchant was so shocked

30:42.570 --> 30:44.630
that he was completely dumbfounded.

30:49.030 --> 30:49.590
Mr. Mao.

30:50.510 --> 30:52.200
For this 30-million project,

30:52.440 --> 30:53.480
you gave us

30:53.480 --> 30:54.750
a lot of help.

30:57.160 --> 30:58.790
Do you think I'm angry?

30:59.790 --> 31:01.680
Am I that petty?

31:02.160 --> 31:03.350
It's just that...

31:03.680 --> 31:05.590
you seem a bit unhappy.

31:06.640 --> 31:07.510
As you know,

31:08.510 --> 31:09.510
Xiaolan

31:09.960 --> 31:11.790
kept me here as a designer

31:12.550 --> 31:14.750
and wanted me to be her teacher.

31:15.920 --> 31:16.880
Do you think

31:17.830 --> 31:19.030
I could agree to that?

31:23.750 --> 31:25.030
To be honest,

31:25.510 --> 31:28.040
after spending time with Xiaolan
these days,

31:28.110 --> 31:30.000
I really like this girl.

31:31.000 --> 31:33.000
She is gifted and talented.

31:33.400 --> 31:34.680
Most importantly,

31:34.680 --> 31:36.830
she has courage and boldness.

31:37.720 --> 31:39.070
Architecture

31:39.070 --> 31:41.110
is not dead. It is alive.

31:41.440 --> 31:43.550
It should grow with the city

31:43.750 --> 31:45.160
and the people.

31:45.920 --> 31:47.160
Xiaolan is so young,

31:47.160 --> 31:48.550
yet she has such vision.

31:48.750 --> 31:50.810
Who wouldn't like a student like her?

31:52.480 --> 31:54.810
Then what are you hesitating for, Mr. Mao?

31:55.160 --> 31:56.200
I am hesitating because,

31:56.200 --> 31:58.550
regarding this 30-million project,

31:58.920 --> 32:00.440
she sees further

32:00.590 --> 32:01.880
than all of us.

32:03.160 --> 32:04.160
I'm old.

32:04.440 --> 32:06.040
How much more can I teach her?

32:07.070 --> 32:08.550
Mr. Mao.

32:09.590 --> 32:10.480
Both proposals

32:10.640 --> 32:11.750
were modified based on

32:11.750 --> 32:12.720
your foundation.

32:12.720 --> 32:13.790
If I were to

32:14.000 --> 32:15.350
start completely from scratch

32:15.350 --> 32:16.720
and create a five-star hotel's

32:16.720 --> 32:17.400
design plan on my own,

32:17.400 --> 32:19.000
I definitely couldn't do it.

32:20.110 --> 32:21.510
Now you're being modest.

32:22.640 --> 32:23.640
It's true.

32:24.030 --> 32:25.760
Your knowledge and experience

32:26.240 --> 32:27.920
are something I could never catch up to,

32:27.920 --> 32:28.960
even if I spent

32:28.960 --> 32:30.420
ten-plus years studying.

32:30.830 --> 32:31.590
Mr. Mao,

32:32.150 --> 32:33.410
I just have foresight,

32:33.790 --> 32:35.200
but I haven't actually walked

32:35.200 --> 32:36.130
much of the path.

32:37.480 --> 32:38.240
So, Mr. Mao,

32:38.960 --> 32:40.480
I really need you.

32:42.710 --> 32:44.110
I want to be your student.

32:45.920 --> 32:47.200
To be my student,

32:47.620 --> 32:49.970
you'd have to kowtow formally.

32:50.350 --> 32:51.010
No problem.

32:54.590 --> 32:55.640
I'll take you.

32:58.470 --> 33:01.530
Congratulations, Ms. Xia!
Congratulations, Mr. Mao!

33:03.440 --> 33:04.970
Congratulations, Mr. Mao!

33:05.000 --> 33:05.920
So you guys

33:06.160 --> 33:07.310
planned it all out.

33:14.240 --> 33:15.880
Tomorrow, I'll go to Dongfeng first.

33:15.880 --> 33:17.070
You go to the law firm.

33:17.070 --> 33:17.640
Then in the afternoon,

33:17.640 --> 33:18.880
let's meet at the Civil Affairs Bureau.

33:18.880 --> 33:19.210
Okay.

33:20.030 --> 33:21.240
After we get the certificate,

33:21.240 --> 33:22.750
let's have dinner together.

33:22.750 --> 33:24.750
Let's invite Wei and Zhenzhu along.

33:25.440 --> 33:25.830
Okay.

33:27.490 --> 33:29.480
Why is Mr. Zhou,
who's usually so sharp-tongued,

33:29.480 --> 33:30.940
only saying "okay" today?

33:31.440 --> 33:32.700
As long as I'm with you,

33:33.110 --> 33:34.710
everything seems fine to me.

33:36.310 --> 33:37.640
Mr. Mao once asked me,

33:38.310 --> 33:39.030
as

33:39.310 --> 33:41.240
a one-in-a-million lucky person,

33:41.510 --> 33:42.920
what right I had to pave the way

33:42.920 --> 33:44.240
for others' futures.

33:45.080 --> 33:47.000
I remember the first time
I went to Longcheng

33:47.000 --> 33:48.270
and met Bai Zhenzhu.

33:48.510 --> 33:49.160
I told her

33:49.160 --> 33:51.070
she could set up a stall in Shengcheng,

33:51.070 --> 33:52.030
and I really thought of myself

33:52.030 --> 33:53.160
as a savior.

33:53.750 --> 33:54.880
Later I realized,

33:55.350 --> 33:56.350
maybe without me,

33:56.680 --> 33:58.590
they would have succeeded anyway.

33:58.590 --> 34:00.440
Just by a different path,

34:01.000 --> 34:02.270
or at a different time.

34:03.200 --> 34:05.400
I'm actually not that important at all.

34:06.440 --> 34:07.840
To other people's lives,

34:08.440 --> 34:10.440
of course we aren't that important.

34:11.360 --> 34:12.440
But you don't need to

34:12.440 --> 34:13.400
completely deny

34:13.400 --> 34:14.530
your contribution.

34:15.110 --> 34:16.710
You really did help Zhenzhu.

34:16.840 --> 34:18.100
And you helped Wei too.

34:18.440 --> 34:19.300
But similarly,

34:19.710 --> 34:20.840
they helped you too.

34:21.679 --> 34:22.320
We have long since

34:22.320 --> 34:23.380
left deep marks

34:23.880 --> 34:25.190
in each other's lives.

34:26.360 --> 34:27.760
They can never be erased.

34:28.880 --> 34:30.230
If I disappear,

34:31.150 --> 34:33.030
will those marks still exist?

34:35.190 --> 34:35.989
What's wrong?

34:36.360 --> 34:37.710
Why are you suddenly looking at me

34:37.710 --> 34:39.040
with such adoring eyes?

34:42.630 --> 34:44.230
Sometimes I really feel like

34:44.800 --> 34:45.440
there are

34:46.230 --> 34:47.670
2 souls in here.

34:48.510 --> 34:49.920
One is the current you,

34:50.440 --> 34:51.190
and the other

34:51.510 --> 34:53.110
is a very mature old soul.

34:56.070 --> 34:56.800
Oh, no.

34:57.510 --> 34:58.510
You think I'm old.

34:58.930 --> 34:59.630
I remember when we

34:59.630 --> 35:00.480
first met,

35:00.480 --> 35:02.190
didn't you think I was childish?

35:02.190 --> 35:03.550
You're still childish now.

35:03.550 --> 35:04.480
Childish and old

35:04.630 --> 35:05.960
aren't contradictory.

35:06.440 --> 35:07.370
Then tomorrow,

35:07.400 --> 35:09.630
do you want a childish me

35:09.760 --> 35:10.880
or an old me?

35:13.070 --> 35:14.760
I want

35:15.710 --> 35:16.570
a handsome you.

35:18.000 --> 35:18.530
Alright.

35:18.710 --> 35:20.070
Then just wait and see.

35:20.800 --> 35:21.190
Okay.

35:34.630 --> 35:35.190
Zhenzhu.

35:36.230 --> 35:38.070
Why do you look more anxious than I do?

35:38.070 --> 35:39.110
Aren't you anxious?

35:39.110 --> 35:40.670
I don't believe you're not anxious.

35:40.670 --> 35:41.710
Why isn't Cheng here yet?

35:41.710 --> 35:42.880
Did something happen on the way

35:42.880 --> 35:43.440
that delayed him?

35:43.440 --> 35:44.300
Did he call you?

35:44.920 --> 35:47.000
No call means he's fine.

35:47.480 --> 35:48.810
Let's wait a bit longer.

35:52.840 --> 35:53.400
Xiaolan.

35:53.760 --> 35:55.420
Something happened to Cheng.

35:55.550 --> 35:56.750
He's in the hospital.

35:57.950 --> 35:58.800
What happened?

35:58.800 --> 35:59.360
Xiaolan!

36:01.030 --> 36:02.490
Why do the people I cherish

36:02.840 --> 36:05.400
always get into trouble
at the most important moments?

36:05.400 --> 36:06.530
Once is an accident.

36:06.840 --> 36:08.170
But twice? Three times?

36:09.630 --> 36:12.030
And my increasingly confused memories...

36:12.840 --> 36:14.320
All of this makes me suspect

36:13.090 --> 36:16.270
[In Operation]

36:14.710 --> 36:16.320
that I've stayed here too long,

36:16.320 --> 36:17.160
done too much,

36:17.440 --> 36:19.840
and affected the balance
of time and space.

36:20.960 --> 36:21.620
Zhou Cheng.

36:22.920 --> 36:24.550
Please be fine.

36:24.960 --> 36:25.670
Make way!

37:29.510 --> 37:30.280
I'm fine.

37:59.590 --> 38:00.190
Jiang Yan!

38:02.510 --> 38:03.110
Jiang Yan!

38:03.960 --> 38:06.280
Jiang Yan! Jiang Yan! Jiang Yan!

38:11.760 --> 38:12.360
Jiang Yan!

38:24.400 --> 38:25.000
Jiang Yan!

38:25.670 --> 38:26.730
Jiang Yan, wake up!

38:30.280 --> 38:31.280
Get up, Jiang Yan!

38:43.070 --> 38:44.410
Leave me. Go!

39:02.710 --> 39:03.240
Xiaolan.

39:05.440 --> 39:06.900
I'm actually very scared.

39:08.110 --> 39:08.960
From Shi Kai,

39:10.480 --> 39:11.230
to Jiang Yan—

39:12.920 --> 39:13.630
if I hadn't insisted

39:13.630 --> 39:15.760
on investigating the fisherman case,

39:16.630 --> 39:17.230
and if I hadn't insisted

39:17.230 --> 39:18.230
on digging deeper,

39:18.230 --> 39:19.110
maybe they wouldn't have...

39:19.110 --> 39:19.770
Zhou Cheng.

39:20.550 --> 39:21.440
You wanted to get justice

39:21.440 --> 39:22.480
for Shi Kai.

39:23.400 --> 39:24.460
That wasn't wrong.

39:26.550 --> 39:27.190
Trust me.

39:28.630 --> 39:29.830
It was not your fault.

39:38.590 --> 39:41.480
Kang Wei, Shi Kai, and Jiang Yan.

39:42.190 --> 39:44.030
These bizarre events

39:44.670 --> 39:46.670
have made Zhou Cheng blame himself.

39:47.280 --> 39:49.000
I know it's not his fault.

39:50.320 --> 39:51.710
All of this

39:52.630 --> 39:54.590
is probably related to my arrival.

39:56.190 --> 39:57.360
But I can't

39:57.710 --> 39:59.570
tell Zhou Cheng about my worries.

40:00.710 --> 40:02.920
I just hope he stays safe,

40:03.630 --> 40:05.880
and these things stop happening.

40:07.510 --> 40:08.190
Be careful.

40:13.550 --> 40:15.070
The surgery went smoothly.

40:15.070 --> 40:15.880
The doctor said

40:15.880 --> 40:17.340
Jiang Yan is out of danger.

40:18.070 --> 40:19.150
But the burns on her back

40:19.150 --> 40:20.150
are quite severe.

40:21.030 --> 40:22.230
We aren't her family.

40:22.880 --> 40:23.960
Her future treatment

40:23.960 --> 40:25.840
requires her parents' involvement.

40:25.840 --> 40:27.440
I've already notified them.

40:28.630 --> 40:30.630
You are Zhou Cheng from Bed 2, right?

40:30.850 --> 40:31.160
Yes.

40:31.190 --> 40:32.490
Visiting hours are over.

40:32.490 --> 40:35.220
Non-family members,
please leave immediately.

40:35.850 --> 40:36.590
Family members only.

40:36.590 --> 40:37.650
Are you her family?

40:38.820 --> 40:40.130
I... sort of am.

40:40.670 --> 40:41.440
Sort of?

40:41.630 --> 40:42.710
So you're not, then.

40:42.710 --> 40:43.840
Come back tomorrow.

40:44.840 --> 40:45.480
It's okay.

40:45.960 --> 40:46.960
You go back first.

40:51.360 --> 40:51.760
Okay.

40:52.360 --> 40:53.420
I'll head off then.

40:53.630 --> 40:54.000
Okay.

41:00.840 --> 41:02.110
I'm leaving now.

41:02.710 --> 41:04.110
I'll come back tomorrow.

41:04.360 --> 41:04.760
Okay.

41:21.480 --> 41:22.140
Zhou Cheng,

41:22.320 --> 41:24.180
you should go back and rest early.

41:48.350 --> 41:48.920
Ms. Xia.

41:50.150 --> 41:51.710
Are you going to the office
tomorrow morning?

41:51.710 --> 41:52.910
Come early tomorrow.

41:53.150 --> 41:54.400
We'll go to the company first,
then the hospital.

41:54.400 --> 41:54.840
Got it.
